        <div class="role-item"><span class="role-num">2</span><p><strong>SOPs from walkthroughs:</strong> record how a process is done once, and turn the transcript into a documented procedure the whole team can follow.</p></div>
        <div class="role-item"><span class="role-num">3</span><p><strong>Anomaly spotting:</strong> ask plain-language questions about weekly numbers and get answers that would otherwise wait for the analyst's availability.</p></div>
